      "id": 81,
      "name": "Mafia Lord's Son Has Secret Love For His Stepmom",
      "description": "Bianca's father is betrayed by his best friend and business partner. He vows to take revenge and proceeds to seek help from Don Pedro, the Mafia Lord. Bianca is brought to Don Pedro and he tells Rocco to leave her behind as collateral of his promise. Enzo is Don Pedro's son who falls in love with Bianca from the first day he saw her, he is appalled and disgusted by his father's actions. Bianca pretends to also be in love with Enzo and they begin to scheme a plan of escape...",
